independent_work.en:
Before each practice session, students are expected to:

* Watch the video lectures available through courses.cs.ut.ee;
* Complete a quiz in Moodle;
* Solve programming assigments and submit the solutions.

Additionally, throughout the course, students will work on a group project.

independent_work.et:
Enne iga praktikumi tuleb:

* Vaadata läbi videoloengud, mis on kättesaadavad courses.cs.ut.ee kaudu;
* Lahendada test Moodle'is;
* Lahendada programmeerimisülesanded ja esitada lahendused.

Lisaks on aines rühmatööna tehtav projekt.
